enableSpokeCaliber.t.sol
├── when call is reentrant
│  └── it should revert with ReentrancyGuardReentrantCall
└── when call is not reentrant
   ├── when caller does not have the relevant role
   │  └── it should revert with AccessManagedUnauthorized
   └── when caller has the relevant role
      ├── given no spoke caliber is registered in this contract for the provided chain ID
      │  └── it should revert with InvalidChainId
      └── given a spoke caliber is registered in this contract for the provided chain ID
         ├── given the spoke caliber is already enabled
         │  └── it should revert with AlreadyEnabled
         └── given the spoke caliber is not already enabled
            ├── it should mark the spoke caliber as enabled
            └── it should emit a SpokeCaliberMailboxEnabled event
